snippet: The rookie Matt Harvey threw six solid innings, but the Giants were carried by a revitalized Tim Lincecum, who struck out seven in seven innings.
lead_paragraph: The rookie Matt Harvey threw six solid innings, but the Giants were carried by a revitalized Tim Lincecum, who struck out seven in seven innings.
